  <brief_title>The Benefits of Early Initiation of Continual Renal Replacement Therapy in Patients With Severe Sepsis</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Benefits of Early Initiation of Continuous Renal Replacement Therapy (CRRT) in Patients With Severe Sepsis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
